headline: Kenvue Tops Q4 Earnings Estimates, Advances Toward Kimberly-Clark Deal

headline: Kimberly-Clark Kenvue Deal Progress Raises Integration And Debt Questions
summary: Kimberly-Clark (NasdaqGS:KMB) is moving ahead with its planned acquisition of Kenvue as the consumer health company begins a global workforce reduction tied to the transaction. Kenvue's restructuring, including significant job cuts, is being positioned as preparation for integration with Kimberly-Clark.
